<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation to Join TracèSys</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-50: #f5f3ff;
            --primary-75: #efe9ff;
            --primary-100: #e5dcff;
            --primary-500: #8b5cf6;
            --primary-600: #7c3aed;
            --primary-700: #5b21b6;
            --text-strong: #0f172a;
            --text-muted: #4c4f6b;
            --border: #e4e2f7;
            --brand-gradient: linear-gradient(120deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7, #c084fc);
        }
        body {
            font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf9ff 0%, #ffffff 30%, #f1f5ff 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 28px 14px;
            color: var(--text-strong);
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .shell {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 32px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 55px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }
        .pill-pill {
            background: #f7edff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.15);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-700);
        }
        .detail-card {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
        }
        .info-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12);
            border-radius: 22px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08);
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 18px 42px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background-color: #7c3aed;
            background-image: var(--brand-gradient);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: 200% 200%;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 55px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35);
        }
        .mobile-stack {
            display: block !important;
            width: 100% !important;
        }
        .mobile-center {
            text-align: center !important;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 8px 4px !important;
            }
            .card {
                border-radius: 16px !important;
            }
            .mobile-padding {
                padding: 20px 16px !important;
            }
            .mobile-padding-sm {
                padding: 14px 12px !important;
            }
            .mobile-h1 {
                font-size: 22px !important;
                line-height: 1.3 !important;
                word-wrap: break-word !important;
            }
            .mobile-h2 {
                font-size: 17px !important;
            }
            .mobile-text {
                font-size: 13px !important;
                word-wrap: break-word !important;
            }
            .mobile-pill {
                display: block !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
                margin-bottom: 8px !important;
                text-align: center !important;
                box-sizing: border-box !important;
                word-wrap: break-word !important;
                word-break: break-word !important;
            }
            .mobile-logo {
                display: block !important;
                margin: 0 auto 12px !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
            }
            .mobile-logo-cell {
                display: block !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
                text-align: center !important;
            }
            .mobile-button {
                display: block !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
                padding: 14px 20px !important;
                font-size: 14px !important;
                text-align: center !important;
                box-sizing: border-box !important;
            }
            .mobile-full-width {
                width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
            }
            .mobile-stack {
                display: block !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
            }
            table {
                max-width: 100% !important;
                width: 100% !important;
            }
            td {
                word-wrap: break-word !important;
                word-break: break-word !important;
            }
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body {
                background: #0b1120;
            }
            .hero-card,
            .content-card,
            .cta-card {
                background: #111830;
                border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            p,
            .detail-value,
            .steps-card,
            .footer {
                color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            }
            .pill {
                background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.18);
                color: #ede9fe;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-collapse:collapse;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:700px; width:100%; border-collapse:separate; border-spacing:0 16px; box-sizing:border-box;">
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="card" style="border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.25); background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(124,58,237,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.95));">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="mobile-padding" style="padding:36px 34px;">
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-collapse:collapse; max-width:100%;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="mobile-logo-cell" width="72" valign="top" style="padding-right:16px; max-width:72px;">
                                                    <img src="cid:logo" alt="TracèSys logo" width="60" height="60" class="mobile-logo" style="display:block; border-radius:18px; border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.18); max-width:100%; height:auto;" />
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="mobile-logo-cell" valign="top" style="width:100%; max-width:100%; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">
                                                    <span style="display:inline-block; padding:6px 18px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(124,58,237,0.12); color:var(--primary-700); font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.24em; text-transform:uppercase; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">TracèSys invitation</span>
                                                    <h1 class="mobile-h1" style="font-size:32px; margin:12px 0 6px; line-height:1.25; color:var(--text-strong); word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">You're invited to join as a <strong style="color:var(--primary-700);"><%= role %></strong></h1>
                                                    <p class="mobile-text" style="margin:0; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.6; font-size:15px; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">Accept the invite to unlock onboarding, dashboards, and practicum coordination. We'll guide you through Google sign-in using the email on this invite.</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:16px; border-collapse:collapse;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="mobile-stack mobile-center" width="50%" style="padding:4px 8px; padding-bottom:8px;" align="right">
                                                    <span class="pill-pill mobile-pill" style="display:inline-block; padding:8px 16px; border-radius:999px; background:#f7edff; border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.15); font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--primary-700); word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word; max-width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;">Sent to <%= email %></span>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="mobile-stack mobile-center" width="50%" style="padding:4px 8px;" align="left">
                                                    <span class="pill-pill mobile-pill" style="display:inline-block; padding:8px 16px; border-radius:999px; background:#f7edff; border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.15); font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--primary-700); word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word; max-width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;">Expires in <%= expiresInDays %> day(s)</span>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="card">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="mobile-padding" style="padding:36px 34px 32px;">
                                        <h2 class="mobile-h2" style="font-size:22px; margin:0 0 8px; color:var(--text-strong);">Review &amp; accept</h2>
                                        <p class="mobile-text" style="margin:0 0 22px; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:15px;">Make sure the details look right before continuing.</p>
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-collapse:separate; border-spacing:0; max-width:100%;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="background:var(--primary-75); border:1px dashed var(--border); border-radius:24px; padding:20px 24px; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word; max-width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;">
                                                    <p class="mobile-text" style="margin:0; line-height:1.6; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14px; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">This invite is linked to <strong style="color:var(--text-strong); word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;"><%= email %></strong>. Sign in with Google to connect it instantly.</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>

                                        <% const hasAssignmentDetails = departmentName || sectionName || program || departmentId || sectionId; %>
                                        <% if (hasAssignmentDetails) { %>
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:20px; border-collapse:collapse;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="font-weight:600; color:var(--text-strong); padding-bottom:10px;">Assignment summary</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% if (departmentName || departmentId) { %>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="padding-bottom:10px;">
                                                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="detail-card">
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="padding:14px 18px;">
                                                                <div style="font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:4px;">Department</div>
                                                                <div class="mobile-text" style="font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-strong);"><%= departmentName || departmentId || "Not assigned" %></div>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% } %>
                                            <% if (sectionName || sectionId) { %>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="padding-bottom:10px;">
                                                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="detail-card">
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="padding:14px 18px;">
                                                                <div style="font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:4px;">Section</div>
                                                                <div class="mobile-text" style="font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-strong);"><%= sectionName || sectionId || "Not assigned" %></div>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% } %>
                                            <% if (program) { %>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="padding-bottom:10px;">
                                                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="detail-card">
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="padding:14px 18px;">
                                                                <div style="font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:4px;">Program</div>
                                                                <div class="mobile-text" style="font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-strong);"><%= program %></div>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% } %>
                                        </table>
                                        <% } %>

                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:22px; border-collapse:separate; border-spacing:0 12px;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="info-card">
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="padding:18px 22px;">
                                                                <strong style="display:block; margin-bottom:4px; color:var(--text-strong);">Security note</strong>
                                                                <span class="mobile-text" style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14px; line-height:1.5;">Your invite token is stored securely so only you can complete onboarding.</span>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="info-card">
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="padding:18px 22px;">
                                                                <strong style="display:block; margin-bottom:4px; color:var(--text-strong);">Need assistance?</strong>
                                                                <span class="mobile-text" style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14px; line-height:1.5;">Reply to this email or message your coordinator if any detail looks off.</span>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" class="card">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="mobile-padding" style="padding:32px;" align="center">
                                        <a class="cta-button mobile-button" href="<%= invitationUrl %>" style="display:inline-block; padding:18px 42px; border-radius:999px; background-color:#7c3aed; background-image:var(--brand-gradient); background-repeat:no-repeat; background-size:200% 200%; color:#ffffff !important; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:0.02em; box-shadow:0 25px 55px rgba(124,58,237,0.35); max-width:100%; box-sizing:border-box; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">Accept invitation &amp; sign in</a>
                                        <p class="mobile-text" style="margin:16px 0 0; font-size:13px; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.5; word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-word;">
                                            Having trouble with the button? Copy and paste this link:<br />
                                            <a class="fallback-link" href="<%= invitationUrl %>" style="color:var(--primary-600); text-decoration:underline; word-break:break-all; word-wrap:break-word; max-width:100%;"><%= invitationUrl %></a>
                                        </p>
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:24px; border:1px dashed var(--border); border-radius:24px; background:rgba(124,58,237,0.05);">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="mobile-padding-sm" style="padding:24px;">
                                                    <p class="mobile-text" style="margin:0 0 8px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-strong); font-size:15px;">What happens next?</p>
                                                    <ol class="mobile-text" style="margin:0; padding-left:18px; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.6; font-size:14px;">
                                                        <li>Click the button above.</li>
                                                        <li>Sign in with your Google account.</li>
                                                        <li>Complete onboarding in just a few minutes.</li>
                                                    </ol>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                        <div class="footer mobile-text" style="margin-top:16px; text-align:center; font-size:13px; color:var(--text-muted);">
                                            <p style="margin:0;">Need help? Reach out to your coordinator or the TracèSys admin desk.</p>
                                            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><small>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore it.</small></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
